<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= user.name %> - Profile</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/Me.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/navbar.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    <div class="profile-card">
    <div class="profile-header">
        <% if(user.avatar){ %>
            <img src="/<%= user.avatar %>" 
                alt="Profile Picture" class="profile-img">
        <% } else { %>
            <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/128/9131/9131529.png" 
                 alt="Default Avatar" class="profile-img">
        <% } %>

        <div class="profile-details">
            <h2><%= user.name %></h2>
            <p class="email"><%= user.email %></p>
            
            <p class="count">Total Links generated: <%= user.links_count %></p>
            <p class="createdAt">member since: <%= user.created_at %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="verification-status">
            <p>Email Verified: 
            <% if(user.is_email_valid) { %>
                <span class="verified">✓ Verified</span>
            <% } else { %>
                <a href="/profile/verify/email" class="verify-link">Verify Now</a>
            <% } %>
            </p>
        </div>
        <p class="desc">
            A motivated person is characterized by their drive to achieve goals, 
        their proactive nature, and their resilience in the face of challenges. 
        They possess a strong sense of purpose, are willing to take risks, and 
        exhibit enthusiasm and dedication to their tasks. These individuals are 
        often self-aware, adaptable, and committed to continuous learning and growth.
    </p>
</div>
<div class="action-buttons">
<a href="/profile/edit" class="btn btn-edit">✏️ Edit Profile</a>
<% if(user.passwordHash){%>
    <a href="/profile/reset-password" class="btn btn-password">🔑 reset Password</a>
<%}else {%>
    <a href="/profile/set-password" class="btn btn-password">🔑 Set Password</a>
<%}%>
<a href="/logout" class="btn btn-logout">⏻ Logout</a>
</div>

</body>
</html>
